lines.p:
Praise Jah!
Offer praise, you servants of Jehovah,Praise the name of Jehovah.
May Jehovah’s name be praisedFrom now on and forever.
From the rising of the sun to its setting,Let Jehovah’s name be praised.
Jehovah is high above all the nations;His glory is above the heavens.
Who is like Jehovah our God,The one who dwells on high?
He stoops down to look on heaven and earth,

Raising the lowly from the dust.
He lifts up the poor from the ash heap
In order to make him sit with nobles,With the nobles of his people.

He gives the barren woman a homeAs a happy mother with children.
Praise Jah!
